The invention relates to a method for editing wireless transmission information for electronic display, wherein a PC under an internet is adopted as a hardware environment in the method. The method comprises the following steps: (1) carrying out system setting; (2) inputting or downloading a text file displayed by an electronic display screen by a computer; (3) inspecting whether text input or text downloading is finished or not, switching to the step (2) if the text input or the text downloading is not finished, and entering a step (4) if the text input or the text downloading is finished; (4) setting a display mode to an edited text file; (5) carrying out the analog display on the set text file, and switching to the step (4) if the text file does not accord with the display mode requirement, and switching to a step (6) if the text file accords with the display mode requirement; and (6) compressing the text file to generate a wireless transmission special format file. In the invention, the special format text file which can transmit real-time information into a wireless device by a GPRS or CDMA network is generated and displayed on the electronic display screen; the contents and the display modes of the electronic display screen can be flexibly changed; and the file generated by the method has high compression ratio, small occupying space and easy wireless transmission.
